00058   class QualifierString : public Qualifier {
00059   public:
00060     QualifierString(QualifierSpec &spec) : Qualifier(spec) {
00061       HT_ASSERT(size > 0);
00062       m_render_buf.reset( new char [ size + 1 ] );
00063       ((char *)m_render_buf.get())[ size ] = 0;
00064     }
00065     virtual ~QualifierString() { }
00066     virtual bool next() {
00067       if (charset.length() > 0)
00068         Random::fill_buffer_with_random_chars((char *)m_render_buf.get(), size, charset.c_str());
00069       else
00070         Random::fill_buffer_with_random_ascii((char *)m_render_buf.get(), size);
00071       m_qualifier = m_render_buf.get();
00072       return false;
00073     }
00074     virtual String &get() { return m_qualifier; }
00075   private:
00076     boost::shared_array<const char> m_render_buf;
00077     String m_qualifier;
00078   };
